data: {"sequence_number": null, "type": "response.output_item.done", "item": {"id": "msg_0d433dfe8cd443ca9f4b1ae90ec0f708", "response_id": "resp_7ea58f3aa6964dbf9f00fe02", "type": "message", "status": "completed", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "output_text", "text": "Let the unknown number be **x**.\n\n**Set up the equation**\n\n\u201cDoubled and added 4\u201d means:\n\n\\[\n2x + 4 = 30\n\\]\n\n**Solve**\n\nSubtract 4 from both sides:\n\n\\[\n2x = 26\n\\]\n\nDivide both sides by 2:\n\n\\[\nx = 13\n\\]\n\n**Check**\n\n\\(2 \\times 13 + 4 = 26 + 4 = 30\\) \u2713\n\n**Final answer: 13**"}], "model": "cursor"}}

